name: Miss Italia metal purse
description:
LYDRA

A stylish metal purse with plenty of space to hold your secret treasures. This one-of-a-kind purse is made from pre-loved fabrics and a surprise lining

Miss Italia looks like a beloved relative :)

Length 14cm
Opening 20cm
Base 26cm
Pocket on inside for your cards and coins
Detachable metal chain 56cm

Each Lydra product comes with a booklet including its own novel name and personality chosen by its maker. There is also a bio on its personal maker!


CARE
Each product is made from preloved fabrics. Preloved fabrics may come with wear ‘n’ tear, fading or marks. This is part of the story that they tell. Use an upholstery protector (such as Scotchgard) to reduce stains.
Please treat your Lydra treasure kindly and with care. Please don’t over fill your Lydra bag and open carefully. Avoid getting your Lydra bag wet as colours may run. Remember that lighter colours mark more easily, so please avoid contact with grease and grime.

name: Miss Celine 3-in-1 clutch

A modular bag that can be worn in many different ways. With detachable straps, you can wear it as a satchel or as a clutch, and you can flip it to have a different colour option.

Option 2: A clutch with/without straps with fabric choice 1.
Option 3: A clutch with/without straps with fabric choice 2. Simply fold the other way

Miss Celine is from the Rock Pool!

Length 32cm
Width 20cm
Strap is 102cm, which is a combination of an old leather belt and brass chain.
Hidden magnetic clasps so you can fold it either way.
Pocket to hold your belongings made from the original leather jacket pocket.
